quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  9,14,"Enti mone wֽ»n nko, na Nyankopֽ»n nam mo nsa so b־µtwe wֽ»n aso, na Wagu wֽ»n anim ase, na Wama mo wֽ»n so nkonimdie, na Wadwodwo amanfoֽ» no a wֽ»gyidie no akoma;"
  9,15,"Na Wayi wֽ»n akoma mu abufuo afiri hֽ». Nyankopֽ»n de nea ֶ†p־µ bֽ»ne b־µky־µ no; na Nyankopֽ»n ne Onimdefoֽ» a ֶ†nim biribiara, ֶ†ne Onyansafoֽ»."
  9,16,"Anaa modwen s־µ y־µbֹ›gyae mo (saa ara) aber־µ a Nyankopֽ»n (ny־µ־µ mo nsֽ»hw־µ) nhunuu mo mu wֽ»n a wֽ»bֽ» mmֽ»den na wֽ»mfiri Nyankopֽ»n ne Ne somafoֽ» ne agyidiefoֽ» no akyi mfa yֽ»nkoֽ»?. Onyankopֽ»n ne dwuma a modie no nyinaa ho Amane bֽ»foֽ»."
  9,17,"Abosomsomfoֽ» no nni ho kwan s־µ wֽ»sra anaas־µ wֽ»y־µ Nyankopֽ»n Nyame-dan (Kaג€™aba) no ho adwuma aber־µ a wֽ»di wֽ»n ara wֽ»n ho adanse־µ s־µ wֽ»wֽ» boniay־µ mu. Saa nkorֽ»foֽ» no na wֽ»n nnwuma ay־µ kwa, na Ogya no mu na wֽ»b־µtena."
  9,18,"Obi a ־µs־µs־µ ֽ»sra anaa ֽ»y־µ Nyankopֽ»n Nyamedan (Kaג€™aba) no ho adwuma ne obi a wagye Nyankopֽ»n ne Da a edi akyire no adie, na ֽ»fr־µ Nyame wֽ» neber־µ mu, na oyi Zaka no, na ֽ»nsuro (obiara) gyes־µ Nyankopֽ»n. Enti ebia saa nkorֽ»foֽ» no na wֽ»b־µka ateneneefoֽ» no ho."
  9,19,"Mode obi a ֽ»ma Hajifoֽ» no nsuo, na ֹ”siesie anaa ֽ»y־µ Nyamedan kronkron no ho adwuma no toto obia wagye Nyankopֽ»n ne Da a edi akyire no adie, na ֽ»ko wֽ» Nyankopֽ»n kwan soֽ» no ho s־µ wֽ»y־µ p־µp־µ־µp־µ? Wֽ»ny־µ p־µ wֽ» Nyankopֽ»n anim. Nyankopֽ»n de־µ ֶ†nkyer־µ nnipa bֽ»nefoֽ» no kwan."
  9,20,"Wֽ»n a wֽ»agye die na wֽ»tuu amantuo na wֽ»de wֽ»n agyapade־µ ne wֽ»n kraa koo Nyankopֽ»n kwan soֽ» no wֽ» gyinaber־µ a ־µsom bo wֽ» Nyankopֽ»n hֽ». Saa nkorֽ»foֽ» no ne nkonimdifoֽ» no."